=Current roster==\n{{Oakland Raiders roster}}\n\n==Preseason==\nThe Raiders' preseason opponents and schedule will be announced in the spring.\n\n==Regular season==\n<!--===Schedule===-->\n===2020 opponents===\nListed below are the Raiders' opponents for [[2020 NFL season|2020]]. Exact dates and times are normally announced in the spring,<ref>{{cite web |title=2020 Opponents Determined |url=https://nflcommunications.com/Pages/2020-Opponents-Determined.aspx |work=NFL Communications |date=December 30, 2019 |accessdate=December 30, 2019}}</ref>however due to the ongoing [[2019-20 coronavirus pandemic in the United States|COVID-19 pandemic]] it is no longer considered certain that the NFL will release its schedule at the usual time nor that season will be played as originally scheduled.\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Las Vegas Raiders|year=2020|border=2}}\"| Category !! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Las Vegas Raiders|year=2020|border=2}}\" width=200px| Home !! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Las Vegas Raiders|year=2020|border=2}}\" width=200px| Away\n|-\n| '''Division opponents'''<br>([[AFC West]]) || colspan=2| [[2020 Denver Broncos season|Denver Broncos]]<br>[[2020 Kansas City Chiefs season|Kansas City Chiefs]]<br>[[2020 Los Angeles Chargers season|Los Angeles Chargers]]\n|-\n| '''Conference opponents'''<br>([[AFC East]]) || [[2020 Buffalo Bills season|Buffalo Bills]]<br>[[2020 Miami Dolphins season|Miami Dolphins]] || [[2020 New England Patriots season|New England Patriots]]<br>[[2020 New York Jets season|New York Jets]]\n|-\n| '''Conference opponents'''<br>(based on {{nfly|2019}} division placement) || [[2020 Indianapolis Colts season|Indianapolis Colts]]|| [[2020 Cleveland Browns season|Cleveland Browns]]\n|-\n| '''Interconference opponents'''<br>([[NFC South]]) || [[2020 New Orleans Saints season|New Orleans Saints]]<br>[[2020 Tampa Bay Buccaneers season|Tampa Bay Buccaneers]] || [[2020 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta Falcons]]<br>[[2020 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina Panthers]]\n|}\n<!--\n===Game summaries===\n====Week #: vs. Denver Broncos====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Las Vegas Raiders|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Denver Broncos at Las Vegas Raiders&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Broncos\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=Raiders\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=Allegiant Stadium, Paradise, Nevada\n|attendance=\n|weather=None (indoor stadium)\n|referee=\n|TV=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|reference=\n|scoring=\n|stats=\n}}\n\n====Week #: vs. Kansas City Chiefs====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Las Vegas Raiders|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Kansas City Chiefs at Las Vegas Raiders&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Chiefs\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=Raiders\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=Allegiant Stadium, Paradise, Nevada\n|attendance=\n|weather=None (indoor stadium)\n|referee=\n|TV=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|reference=\n|scoring=\n|stats=\n}}\n\n====Week #: vs. Los Angeles Chargers====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Las Vegas Raiders|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Los Angeles Chargers at Las Vegas Raiders&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Chargers\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=Raiders\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=Allegiant Stadium, Paradise, Nevada\n|attendance=\n|weather=None (indoor stadium)\n|referee=\n|TV=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|reference=\n|scoring=\n|stats=\n}}\n\n====Week #: vs. Buffalo Bills====\n{{Americanfootballbox\n|titlestyle={{NFLPrimaryStyle|Las Vegas Raiders|year=2020|border=2}};text-align:center;\n|state=autocollapse\n|title=Week #: Buffalo Bills at Las Vegas Raiders&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n|date=\n|time=\n|road=Bills\n|R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0\n|home=Raiders\n|H1=0|H2=0|H3=0|H4=0\n|stadium=Allegiant Stadium, Paradise, Nevada\n|attend